oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph album containing souvenir photographs from France
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph album of souvenir photographs from France during World War I. Each photograph has a caption and typically 4 photographs per page, some pages differ. One photograph depicts Gen. John Pershing and Marshal Joseph Joffre.
